{"id": "art-137", "label": "Art. 137", "title": "Art. 137", "slug": "art-137", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 137 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_465449074\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2259\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_465449074\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Societatea pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\neste administrat&#259; de unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span>\nadministratori, num&#259;rul acestora fiind totdeauna impar. Când sunt mai <span\nclass=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> administratori, ei constituie un consiliu de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2006057859\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2258\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2006057859\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> ale c&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ii</span>\nfinanciare anuale fac obiectul unei <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span>\nlegale de auditare sunt administrate de cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n3 administratori.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_77150100\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2257\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_77150100\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> prezentei <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i> cu privire la consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> care\nnu privesc sau nu presupun pluralitatea administratorilor se aplic&#259;\nadministratorului unic în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}